<section class="article135" data-role="outer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">不期朱夏尽，凉吹暗迎秋。江西软件职业技术大学在9月14号至16号，又迎来了一批崭新的面孔-----23级专科新生。江西软件职业技术大学的迎新工作正式拉开帷幕。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-21%2016%3A33%3A23%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20230921163148.jpg?Expires=2010645203&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=E1KtiX76jZAtFgax0qr64Vg4oWA%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学校领导极其重视迎新工作，对迎新相关事宜做出了重要指示，队迎新工作者进行了相关培训，充分保障服务质量，以确保新生顺利入学，有了本科迎新的经验，此次专科迎新显得更加井然有序，尽可能满足新生及家长的需求。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">微笑服务，注重人文关怀</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学校考虑到同学们经过舟车劳顿，疲惫不堪，为此学校特地设立了免费的饮水摊位，方便新生及家长。面对新生们提出的诸多问题，志愿者不厌其烦的为其一一解答，始终保持微笑，这不但让新生们倍感亲切，更体现出我校学生的高素质修养，学院领导也多次来看望，慰问新生、家长以及志愿者。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-21%2016%3A33%3A55%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20230921163148_2.jpg?Expires=2010645235&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=StMvo2bT0H88adR9XrEiB7MCHys%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p></section><p><section class="article135" data-role="outer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">智慧迎新，提高工作质量</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学校充分发挥软件大学的优势，智慧迎新，使用校园通软件及系统，让同学们可以提前上传资料，完成缴费，极大地优化了整个报到流程，招就处的工作人员也提前跟新生进行沟通，进行线上线下联系，获取我们新生的报到行程，有利于我们迎新工作的进行。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-21%2016%3A34%3A11%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20230921163148_1.jpg?Expires=2010645251&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=vB%2BGNRHTteFkufyMIJIk4vi8fQQ%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">贴心服务，展示学院魅力</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">考虑到同学们一路的辛苦，学校安排了200余名志愿者为新生服务，同时学校还设立了茶水摊位，为同学们消暑。志愿者热情地为新生答疑解惑，搬运行李，让大一新生在入学的第一天就深深的感受到江西软件职业技术大学的魅力所在。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">至此，江西软件职业技术大学迎新活动到此圆满结束。相信在之后的学校生活中，大一新生能适应身份的转变，在江软校园绽放出自己的光芒。</span></p></section></p><p><br/></p>